pvalue_df <- read_csv("p_value_50.csv") %>%
  filter(Character %in% freq_df$Character | Character == "家") %>%
  select(Character, contains("sig")) %>%
  drop_na() %>%
  melt(id.vars="Character", variable.name="T1_T2", value.name="Sig") %>%
  mutate(T1_T2=gsub("_sig", "", T1_T2)) %>%
  filter(T1_T2 %in% T1_T2_lst) %>%
  separate(T1_T2, into=c("T1", "T2"), sep="_", remove=FALSE)
## Warning: Missing column names filled in: 'X1' [1]
## 
## ── Column specification ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## cols(
##   .default = col_double(),

## ℹ Use `spec()` for the full column specifications.
comb_df <- pvalue_df %>%
  filter(Sig | Character == "家") %>%
  
  left_join(freq_df) %>%
  filter(T1==Dynasty) %>%
  select(-Dynasty) %>%
  rename(T1_freq=Freq) %>%
  
  left_join(freq_df) %>%
  filter(T2==Dynasty) %>%
  select(-Dynasty) %>%
  rename(T2_freq=Freq) %>%
  
  melt(variable.name="T_freq", value.name="Freq") %>%
  mutate(T_freq=case_when(
    T_freq == "T1_freq" ~ T1,
    T_freq == "T2_freq" ~ T2
  ))
## Joining, by = "Character"
## Joining, by = "Character"
## Using Character, T1_T2, T1, T2, Sig as id variables
comb_df$T2 <- factor(comb_df$T2, levels=T2_lst)
comb_df$T_freq <- factor(comb_df$T_freq, level=dynasty_lst)
comb_df$T1_T2 <- factor(comb_df$T1_T2, level=T1_T2_lst, labels=T1_T2_dash_lst)
Qing_char_lst <- c(pvalue_df %>% filter(T2=="Qing", Sig==TRUE) %>% pull(Character), "家")

new_df <- read_csv("/Users/mac/Documents/in_sync_mac/in_sync_documents/corpus/ASBC/v5_corpus/freq.csv") %>%
  select(-X1, -raw_freq) %>%
  filter(char %in% Qing_char_lst) %>%
  rename(Character=char, T2_freq=relative_freq) %>%
  
  left_join(freq_df) %>%
  filter(Dynasty=="Qing") %>%
  select(-Dynasty) %>%
  rename(T1_freq=Freq) %>%
  
  melt(variable.name="T_freq", value.name="Freq") %>%
  mutate(T_freq=case_when(
    T_freq == "T1_freq" ~ "Qing",
    T_freq == "T2_freq" ~ "1980s"
  )) %>%
  mutate(T1_T2="Qing - 1980s", T1="Qing", T2="1980s")

cum_df <- read_csv("/Users/mac/Documents/in_sync_mac/in_sync_documents/corpus/ASBC/v5_corpus/freq.csv") %>%
  select(-X1) %>%
  rename(Character=char, raw_1980s=raw_freq, relative_1980s=relative_freq) %>%
  
  full_join(read_csv("../[step 3] calc_freq_v0/all.csv"), by="Character") %>%
  select(-X1) %>%

  drop_na() %>%
  mutate(
    prop_Tang=round(raw_Tang/sum(raw_Tang)*100, 3),
    prop_Song=round(raw_Song/sum(raw_Song)*100, 3),
    prop_Yuan=round(raw_Yuan/sum(raw_Yuan)*100, 3),
    prop_Ming=round(raw_Ming/sum(raw_Ming)*100, 3),
    prop_Qing=round(raw_Qing/sum(raw_Qing)*100, 3),
    prop_1980s=round(raw_1980s/sum(raw_1980s)*100, 3)
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    rank_Tang=dense_rank(desc(raw_Tang)),
    rank_Song=dense_rank(desc(raw_Song)),
    rank_Yuan=dense_rank(desc(raw_Yuan)),
    rank_Ming=dense_rank(desc(raw_Ming)),
    rank_Qing=dense_rank(desc(raw_Qing)),
    rank_1980s=dense_rank(desc(raw_1980s))
  ) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_Tang)) %>% mutate(cum_Tang=round(cumsum(raw_Tang)/sum(raw_Tang)*100, 3)) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_Song)) %>% mutate(cum_Song=round(cumsum(raw_Song)/sum(raw_Song)*100, 3)) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_Yuan)) %>% mutate(cum_Yuan=round(cumsum(raw_Yuan)/sum(raw_Yuan)*100, 3)) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_Ming)) %>% mutate(cum_Ming=round(cumsum(raw_Ming)/sum(raw_Ming)*100, 3)) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_Qing)) %>% mutate(cum_Qing=round(cumsum(raw_Qing)/sum(raw_Qing)*100, 3)) %>%
  arrange(desc(raw_1980s)) %>% mutate(cum_1980s=round(cumsum(raw_1980s)/sum(raw_1980s)*100, 3)) %>%
  #write.csv("all_cum.csv")
  filter(Character=="家")
